{"tid":2173032,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[認真討論] 連登仔成日屌9人恐懼撚, 支那肺炎究竟係咪真係感冒咁, just a flu, 無後遺症?","createTime":"2020-08-25T04:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T04:37:10.000Z","uid":334720,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c41cebeed5bc2b5155924b2bdedaa38885995215","tid":2173032,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:07:15.000Z","msg":"見好多POST 成日屌9袁國勇 / 何柏良 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話人恐懼撚 點點點 <br />\n又話後生死亡率低 驚西<br />\n又話球星中肺炎咪又繼續比賽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家擺明全球趨勢真係變左流行病 傳染程度 好似感冒咁<br />\n雖然死亡率低, 但係咪醫好左之後真係好似感冒咁乜事都無先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1) 目前只可以用其他藥治療, 減輕症狀。就算肺好返, 你用個D藥係咪之後無後遺症?<br />\n2) 中肺炎個時。重點唔一定係肺功能受影響, 而係病毒會攻擊埋其他器官, 引起其他併發症。呢個機率係咪同感冒一樣機率咁低? <br />\n<br />\n我記得大家一開始笑9 侵爺話just a flu, 又屌9佢咁講係CLS, 輕視左肺炎威力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家連登反而開始多人屌9D人恐懼撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟係咩logic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果世界真係拎肺炎同感冒 一視同仁拎處理手法, 解除出入境限制, 會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1221743be670027ab0afb23ea59de0f13eff7d9c","tid":2173032,"uid":78574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:08:12.000Z","msg":"勇者應該唔戴口罩出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />戴口罩死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d997b719894e2749d0b6b984f811987f373fb9ae","tid":2173032,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:08:48.000Z","msg":"問題係冇人知點醫武肺"},{"pid":"9030fcf28d7d1bcdc81aa0de9bcc30aab852cbab","tid":2173032,"uid":97551,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:09:14.000Z","msg":"果啲係on9仔黎<br />\n睇到就block"},{"pid":"180f5144501bf3065fea066c7f90b306e33ce390","tid":2173032,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d997b719894e2749d0b6b984f811987f373fb9ae","tid":2173032,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:08:48.000Z","msg":"問題係冇人知點醫武肺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:17:41.000Z","msg":"岩呀 就係無解藥/疫苗<br />\n<br />\n復原方法:<br />\n1) 自癒 : 唔用藥, 靠自己抵抗力毆嬴D病毒<br />\n問題就黎, 你拖咁耐, 係咪真係訓一兩個星期好返咁簡單?<br />\n病情不嬲愈拖得耐, 愈影響身體, 引發其他病既機率更加高<br />\n<br />\n2) 用藥減輕症狀<br />\nD藥你以為係D 一般家庭醫生開既退燒藥, 食完會眼訓 / 攰?<br />\n以為一般抗生素 食完屙尿 黃D臭D就完?"},{"pid":"83ff96b23cb66f9d6e92c1c51091ce4db6bc36b3","tid":2173032,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9030fcf28d7d1bcdc81aa0de9bcc30aab852cbab","tid":2173032,"uid":97551,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:09:14.000Z","msg":"果啲係on9仔黎<br />\n睇到就block"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:19:40.000Z","msg":"個D撚屌應該好好思考下<br />\n如果真係 肺炎 同 感冒 可以相同並論既話<br />\n咁點解各國政府唔拿拿林解除限制呀? <br />\n反正而家爆撚到咁 都補救唔到架啦 由9佢繼續爆丫嘛<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">當初係邊撚個低估肺炎 <br />\n而搞到而家咁呀??</span></span>"},{"pid":"ba4526ae26f81a5e1240488707411e3d70fc089d","tid":2173032,"uid":367147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:20:44.000Z","msg":"呢個病毒係死唔去但係啲後遺症好騎呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30082ddb697f1b33ce5dc1b051af17350e780beb","tid":2173032,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:23:34.000Z","msg":"究竟大家有幾深入去搵下肺炎對身體既影響, <br />\n同埋了解下關於康復有咩後遺症 同 機率有幾大?<br />\n係咪真係可以當感冒咁看待?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YdeoZJr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYdeoZJr.png&h=171648c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a2c30d3dc87891aa4641b1c3256c4b186ab993d","tid":2173032,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba4526ae26f81a5e1240488707411e3d70fc089d","tid":2173032,"uid":367147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:20:44.000Z","msg":"呢個病毒係死唔去但係啲後遺症好騎呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:27:15.000Z","msg":"一種可以引起各種症狀既病毒就係咁先煩<br />\n<br />\n同埋而家器官受損 點可能100%復完到<br />\n例如拗個柴, 到時腳踝好返都係會有少少腫, 莫講話內臟?<br />\n<br />\n有無屌開恐懼撚既人可以一齊討論下?"},{"pid":"f5c52fe741dc9b46cb2bdc0c9ea6df849cf0a186","tid":2173032,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:34:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63f6ac0bc971f9b02c1b32d2daa3a5cce3e114b","tid":2173032,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:34:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1a199c3ca42ed92b48a4ddebcd5feb433bf8f9","tid":2173032,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:37:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}